      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "**The Rosettes foldout, as a whole object.** The nine medallions, their joining causeways, and the six-panel fold structure are properties of the spread *entire* (f85v–86r) — the largest object in the manuscript. Attached to the whole object (no box), so the Viewer frames the foldout rather than pinning one rosette.",
          "purpose": "commenting"
